                           <p>Before investing, consider your investment objectives and Betterment LLC's fees and expenses. Betterment LLC's internet-based advisory services are designed to assist clients in achieving discrete financial goals. They are not intended to provide comprehensive tax advice or financial planning with respect to every aspect of a client's financial situation and do not incorporate specific investments that clients hold elsewhere. For more details, see Betterment’s <a href="agreements/Betterment_LLC_Form_CRS_04_25_2024%20%28FINAL%29-1.pdf"><span>Form CRS</span></a>, <a href="agreements/Betterment_LLC_ADV%20PART%202_2024_10_01-1.pdf"><span>Form ADV Part II</span></a> and <a href="legal-1.html"><span>other disclosures</span></a>.</p>
